category: Python
build-depends: cygport libxsimd-devel python39-beniget python39-gast python39-numpy python39-ply python312-beniget python312-gast python312-numpy python312-ply
sdesc: "ahead of time compiler for numeric kernels for Python"
ldesc: "Pythran is an ahead of time compiler for a subset of the Python language, with a focus on scientific computing. It takes a Python module annotated with a few interface descriptions and turns it into a native Python module with the same interface, but (hopefully) faster."
skip:

homepage: https://github.com/serge-sans-paille/pythran
license: BSD-3-Clause
